    <item>
      <title>Stournaras 表示，欧洲央行应在每次会议中降息，直至利率降至 2%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/ecb-should-cut-each-meeting-until-it-reaches-2-stournaras-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员亚尼斯·斯图纳拉斯 (Yannis Stournaras) 表示，欧洲央行应该在每次会议上降低借贷成本，直到达到既不限制也不刺激经济活动的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/ecb-should-cut-each-meeting-until-it-reaches-2-stournaras-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:53:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着国际货币基金组织的审查继续进行，埃及镑跌至 3 月份以来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/egypt-s-pound-falls-to-lowest-since-march-as-imf-review-goes-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于新兴市场普遍抛售以及当地对美元的需求增加，埃及镑已跌至自 3 月份贬值以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/egypt-s-pound-falls-to-lowest-since-march-as-imf-review-goes-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
